The paper deals with program analysis and automatic repair, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. It specifically focuses on the analysis of program syntax and semantics, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL). The use of neural networks for program analysis and repair also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper's focus on type inference and program compilation suggests a connection to systems and control (cs.SY).
